HEADWORD: Archly
<hw>Arch"ly</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In an arch manner;
with attractive slyness or roguishness; slyly; waggishly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Archly</qex> the maiden smiled.</q>
